tags.name:
simple-datetime
A simple datetime element that takes in unix timestamp and outputs a date.
tags.jsDoc:
/**
 * `simple-datetime`
 * @customElement simple-datetime
 * A simple datetime element that takes in unix timestamp and outputs a date.
 * @demo demo/index.html
 * @microcopy - the mental model for this element
 * - passing in a timestamp from unix and having it be php based date formatting to render is super helpful
 */

attributes.name: unix
attributes.description: Support for UNIX timestamp conversion on the fly

properties.name: unix
properties.description: Support for UNIX timestamp conversion on the fly
